div.div: Feeder: arranges urls into mini queue for each domain, formulates batches to be consumed by spider for a single run
1. Each group contains couple of urls from most important and high priority domains
2. these batches are computed ahead of time
3. Spider ask for feed, feeder shares the batch
4. Spider confirms fetch status in few secs
5. Internally batches are formed basis priority and stored basis priority
6. Batch with highest priority is served first to the spiders
